      "id": "PopularPost322649",
      "post_content": "1. Steal an opponent's creature with [Mind Control](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Control), Control Magic, whatever.  \n2. Cast this card.  \n3. Cast [Mirrorweave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirrorweave), targeting this.  \n4. Activate the stolen creature's version of this card's ability. It gets shuffled into their library (and stops being a copy), then (assuming they're not using this card) their entire library goes into the graveyard.",
      "posted_by": "Aquillion",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost322649\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">1.  Steal an opponent's creature with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mind Control\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mind Control\">Mind Control</a>, Control Magic, whatever.<br/>2.  Cast this card.<br/>3.  Cast <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirrorweave\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirrorweave\">Mirrorweave</a>, targeting this.<br/>4.  Activate the stolen creature's version of this card's ability.  It gets shuffled into their library (and stops being a copy), then (assuming they're not using this card) their entire library goes into the graveyard.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '322649'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy93120\">Aquillion</span>\r\n                                (6/17/2013 8:51:18 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../